		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">A wave of uncertainty follows you. What are your motivations? What&rsquo;s your plan? Whatever the answers, those you oppose are sure to be vexed. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your Dexterity or Charisma score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You may choose to have the bonus damage from your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.4727pnvz5nwn3h23]{Sneak Attack} be psychic damage if you wish. You make this determination whenever you use Sneak Attack.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When you deal psychic damage to a creature by any means, it treats you as lightly obscured until the beginning of your next turn.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">If you fail a check using thieves&rsquo; tools, the disguise kit, the poisoner&rsquo;s kit, or the forgery kit, you can spend a use of bardic inspiration to immediately reroll the check, potentially turning a failure into a success.&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Half your bard levels count as rogue levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.mfqnpwmprkj1dex6]{Guarded Aspect} feature.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
